    "description": [
      "The dirt footpath forks towards both the northwest and northeast, and gives way from packed earth to a mix of smooth stones and ragged grass springing from the ground.  Running alongside the path is a low cracked stone wall, with numerous stones laying fallen along its base.  A series of weeds entangle those stones, while some thicker vines cling to their surfaces."
